data.description: TO BE BUILT! UNDER CONTRACT! MOST CLOSING COSTS PAID by the builder, if under contract by DEC. 31, 2020, using builder's preferred lender (doesn't include FINANCING FEES, BUYERS' PRE-PAIDS, INSURANCE & TAXES)! Open 4 bedroom, 3 bath floor plan featuring wide open Greatroom, kitchen and formal dining room. Boxed ceilings are featured in the greatroom and master bedroom. Perfect split bedroom layout with a 2-car garage. Some upgraded appointments include: granite counter tops throughout, luxury vinyl plank floor tile in the living room, formal dining room and guest hallways, upgraded appliance package and custom tile master shower. Additional features include: brick exterior, custom wood cabinets, designer luxury vinyl plank tile flooring from builder's selection in kitchen and wet areas, chamfer-corner bead, vinyl Low E tilt sash windows and sodded front and side yard with plant package. Upgraded Appliances include: stainless steel dishwasher, electric smooth-top cook top, eye-level oven and microwave and a vented hood. Enjoy a large master bedroom and master bath with a custom tile shower. Plantation Woods is convenient to I-10, Avalon Blvd., and downtown Milton, Florida. Buyer to verify schools, lot size, HOA dues & restrictions, taxes, etc. Call for a modified pricing quote on this model. No restrictions in Plantation Woods subdivision against home owners storing their boat, motor home or camper on their property. Photographs are of a similar model home and may show features & options not included in all models.
